oposed ME-FEEL can achieve an accuracy\ngain up to 32.7% in the industrial IoT networks with the severely limited\nresources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Oct 2021 08:14:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-29"}
