ent\nrank two at most admissible levels. Using logarithmic modules for the $\\beta\n\\gamma$ VOA, we are able to construct logarithmic $L_k(\\mathfrak g)$--modules\nof rank three.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Oct 2021 15:20:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-29"}
